underlying_goal: Archive internal planning documents by renaming them to be descriptive and committing them to the repository.
primary_success: Read the content of eight randomly-named plan files, synthesized a descriptive new filename for each, and performed the renames before committing.
brief_summary: User asked to commit several auto-generated plan files. The agent first identified their nature, then, per user request, read all eight files, renamed them to be descriptive of their content, handled a git rebase, and committed and pushed the renamed files.
